@startuml Component Diagram - Layer 1: Presentation Components (Simplified)
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml
title Layer 1: Presentation Components (Smart Components - UI Only)

Container_Boundary(renderer, "Renderer Process (Angular)") {
    Component(nav_bar,  "Navigation Bar", "Component", "Route navigation")
    Component(side_bar, "Sidebar",        "Component", "DIP tree, document selection")
    Component(workspace_ui, "Workspace UI", "Component", "Import status, progress")
    Component(search_ui, "Search UI", "Component", "Text search interface")
    Component(sema_search_ui, "Semantic Search", "Component", "Semantic search interface")
    Component(dip_tree, "DIP Tree View", "Component", "Document tree display")
    Component(viewer, "Document Viewer", "Component", "Document content display")
    Component(actions, "Document Actions", "Component", "Export, print buttons")
    Component(verification, "Verification UI", "Component", "Integrity check display")
    Component(metadata, "Metadata Panel", "Component", "Document metadata display")
}

note as principles
  **Layer 1: Presentation**
  
  Responsibility: Render UI + user interaction
  
  Each component:
  ✓ Subscribes to RxJS observables
  ✓ Updates local UI state
  ✓ Calls service methods on user action
  ✓ Passes data to child components
  ✗ Does NOT contain business logic
  ✗ Does NOT manage shared state
  
  Pattern: Smart/Container components
  Characteristic: Minimal logic, maximum delegation
end note

@enduml
